ext> </mrow> <mo stretchy=\"false\">(</mo> <mrow> <mtext>m</mtext> </mrow> <mo stretchy=\"false\">)</mo> </math></span>     <strong><em>A1</em></strong></p>\n<p> </p>\n<p>Note:     Award final <strong><em>A1 </em></strong>only if the correct answer has been given to 3 significant figures.</p>\n<p> </p>\n<p><strong><em>[6 marks]</em></strong></p>\n</div>", "examiners_html": "<div class=\"question\">\n[N/A]\n</div>"}